{"tid":2195221,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"律師盧思位下午抵深圳爭取見被扣港人　另有家屬正辦手續","createTime":"2020-09-09T04:39:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-09T11:13:16.000Z","uid":240362,"like":27,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"614d60490198413804127898882224c60d8fb07e","tid":2195221,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T04:39:26.000Z","msg":"12名港人涉嫌非法入境內地水域被截獲，目前正在深圳羈押。受家屬委託的四川律師盧思位，接受本台查詢時表示，今早從成都飛往深圳，預計下午2時再到鹽田看守所爭取會見當事人，他說已經取得家屬的律師委託書公證文件。<br />\n<br />\n另一名受家屬委託的上海律師任全牛接受本台訪問時説，有待家屬在香港辦理公證手續，最快下周才能再到深圳爭取探視。他說內地沒有法律規定，涉及港人的案件需要相關手續，星期一被拒會見之後，已向深圳檢察機關投訴公安機關和看守所。<br />\n<br />\n任全牛表示，當局始終沒有明確告知，如果取得公證文件是否肯定能會見當事人，因此屆時是否能探視仍不樂觀。他又説，家屬從網上聯絡他，亦不想他向傳媒講太多情況，反映他們非常忐忑、焦慮和恐懼，擔心一旦公開當事人名字會被打壓或迫害。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1548652-20200909.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1548652-20200909.htm&d=Yvf7L03l0%2FKFASkGPCPwgwoLTLCpuPbPc66RZsxrzrI%3D&h=3ee33e24\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1548652-20200909.htm&h=ddafbe6a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1548652-20200909.htm</a>"},{"pid":"f53aff7923f827734ea9d9997f8c38ef1c7ef0b9","tid":2195221,"uid":65888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T04:40:20.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"59afb780e54f643c380dc2d755d2c6660a7e8deb","tid":2195221,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T04:40:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe0aa06429b810f63b048d468be5f51775ac0947","tid":2195221,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quot